1. Clone this branch

2. Navigate to IzvorniKod/backend directory

3. Log into Heroku

4. Run "mvn clean heroku:deploy

If you do not have permissions to web-gym2 app on heroku, create your own with "heroku create NAME-OF-APP".
Go to pom.xml and locate "Heroku Maven Plugin Configuration" (Ctrl+f and search)
Change <appName>web-gym2</appName> to <appName>NAME-OF-APP</appName>
Then do step 4

If you make your own app, the frontend service needs to updated with the new deployed backend URL